here we are wokring with 4 layer architecture

1.UI(How my login,logout...Ui will look like)
=>component
=>pages

2.Hook(for managing state and api layers)
=>hooks

3.State(it will store the data that will be coing from UI)
=>auth.context.jsx
=>ai.context.jsx

4.Api(for communication with backend)
=>services
  =>auth.api.js
